        parsed_args={
            'prompt': 'What is the Connectivity Segment Adjusted EBITDA disclosed in the SpaceX S-1 filing {{spacex_s1}}? Provide the exact figures for all periods presented (FY2023, FY2024, FY2025, Q1 2026 if available). Also describe how Connectivity Segment Adjusted EBITDA is defined and whether it is described as the primary internal cash source.'
